    <briefdescription>
<para>Command that updates the heading direction of a GameObject. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This command encapsulates a request to change the heading (facing direction) of a GameObject. It targets the SteeringComponent and applies the specified direction and turn factor (interpolation speed). </para>
